														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2564314">
									

<p>I've mentioned this in chat a few times, but I just want to thank A Random Day for choosing <a href="/scp-847">SCP-847</a> to be a part of this guide. Maintaining clinical tone was incredibly important throughout the piece. Heck, I imagined the Foundation researcher charged with writing this as thinking, &quot;Oh god, stick to the facts, stick to the facts, don't think about her,&quot; throughout the entire piece. Keeping the object dead to you in the prose was key, because the visceral effect was anything but.</p>
<p>The amount of time I spent asking myself if &quot;high-pitched whimpering gasps and adopting more provocative poses&quot; was a reasonable way to describe it trying to come on to a man was huge. Thank you for noticing that.</p>

